      • obtainLayoutData

        @ADeepCloneTestExclude
public TransitionLayoutData obtainLayoutData()
        Returns the layout data for this transition. This data is parsed from the model with each call, so repeated access should be avoided by storing the result in a local variable.

      • obtainLabelData

        @ADeepCloneTestExclude
public LabelLayoutData obtainLabelData()
        Returns the layout data for the label of this transition or null if no label is available. This data is parsed from the model with each call, so repeated access should be avoided by storing the result in a local variable.
